@startuml
!theme silver

title REQ_IVI_015: OTA Failure Auto-Recovery (ASIL-C)

participant "OTA Server" as Server
participant "CAN Bus" as CAN
box "vECU (Target)" #f9f9f9
    participant "OTA_Update_Agent" as OTA
    participant "Flash Memory" as FLASH
    participant "Bootloader" as BL
    participant "DEM" as DEM
end box

== OTA Update in Progress ==

Server -> CAN : 0x36 0A [256 bytes]\n(Block 10/16)
CAN -> OTA : Transfer Data Block 10
activate OTA
OTA -> FLASH : Write to Flash
activate FLASH

== Power Failure Occurs ==

note over FLASH #Red
    **POWER CUT**
    Simulated by CANoe
    Fault Injection
end note

FLASH --> OTA : Write Interrupted
deactivate FLASH
OTA -> OTA : Detect Incomplete Transfer
deactivate OTA

== System Reboot ==

note over BL: **Bootloader Startup**\nPower Restored

BL -> BL : Check Application Integrity
BL -> FLASH : Read Application CRC
activate FLASH
FLASH --> BL : CRC Mismatch\n(Corrupted Application)
deactivate FLASH

BL -> BL : **Recovery Decision**\nApplication Invalid

== Automatic Rollback ==

BL -> FLASH : Load Backup Image\n(Previous Valid Version)
activate FLASH
note right: REQ_IVI_015\nRecovery: 100%

FLASH -> FLASH : Copy Backup to Active\n(Address: 0x90000 → 0x80000)
FLASH --> BL : Rollback Complete
deactivate FLASH

BL -> BL : Verify Backup Integrity
BL -> FLASH : Read Backup CRC
activate FLASH
FLASH --> BL : CRC Valid
deactivate FLASH

== Application Restart ==

BL -> OTA : Start Application\n(Previous Version)
activate OTA

OTA -> OTA : Initialize System
OTA -> DEM : Log Recovery Event\n(DTC: 0xC00500)
activate DEM
DEM --> OTA : Event Logged
deactivate DEM

OTA --> CAN : System Ready\n(Fallback Version Active)
CAN --> Server : Recovery Complete

note over OTA
    **REQ_IVI_015 Verified**
    • Auto Rollback: 100%
    • Previous Version Restored
    • System Functional
    • DTC Logged for Analysis
end note

deactivate OTA

@enduml
